Greek Regulator May Extend Short Selling Ban, Euro2day Says

-- B y   N a t a l i e   W e e k s
-- 
2011-09-29T14:35:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/greek-regulator-may-extend-short-selling-ban-euro2day-says.html
Greece ’s securities regulator is
examining extending a ban on short selling on the Athens
exchange, Euro2day.gr reported, without citing anyone.  The regulator’s ban on short selling from Aug. 9 ends on
Oct. 7 and may be extended by up to 2 months, the Athens-based
news website said.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
